user.biography:
Premium baby necessities made for modern mamas
Organic cotton + buttery soft knit fabrics
swaddles, bibs, 3-layer quilts, gowns, headbands
& more 🤍

node.text:
Please watch and send some ❤️ as we share our story about Jane ❄️

A portion of all our Jane proceeds will be donated to The March of Dimes - which leads the fight for the health of all mothers and babies ❤️

node.text:
It’s AUSSIE time mate! This new collection is one we’ve been so excited to share with you!! We’re so grateful to have Copper Pearl in Australia and we wanted to show our support to all our Aussie friends with this new print! 

Check out the video above and let us know if you have any questions 👇🏼 we hope you ❤️ it as much as we do!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Copper Pearl | Modern Baby on July 17, 2021 tagging @brittanyrcohen. May be an image of 1 person, baby and indoor.

node.text:
Late night mama talk!! This picture fills me with so much joy! Let me tell  you why- these knotted gowns were once a dream that we’ve been able to make come to life 🤍 seeing your little babes wrapped up in them makes the process all worth it! Soooo now tell us- what’s something you DREAM about us coming out with? Like, if you could pick one thing we could launch next week what would it be? ☺️
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
📷 by @brittanyrcohen

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Copper Pearl | Modern Baby on July 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'SLEEP Sale BAG'.

node.text:
RUN! We just dropped 26 sleep bags into our SALE section on our website 🏃🏻‍♀️ Prices as low as $32! If you’ve been wanting to try one of our 3 layer, buttery soft, ultra cozy sleep bags now is the time! 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
About our sleep bags ⬇️
• they have a TOG rating of 1.25. This means the sleep bags are ideal for home temperatures between 65-75° F
• they have a top to bottom zipper for both safety and convenience
• we currently have two sizes: 0-6 months and 6-12 months

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Copper Pearl | Modern Baby on July 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'hellomillia millie'.

node.text:
Our new MILLIE + ZARA expansion is here! Millie is the sweetest colored leopard print that were overly obsessed with! It comes in pretty much everything you could ask for 🙌🏼 we’ve also expanded our Zara print to come in bibs, binky clips, burp cloths, and nylon bows. If you love the orginal cheetah print you can grab this in everything too! 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Tag a mama who needs some darling new goodies and let us know if you have any questions below 👇🏼
